<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TPB Rickyisms</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Kill 2 birds with one stone</h1>
    <form action="/quotes" method="POST">
        <input type="text" placeholder="name" name="name">
        <input type="text" placeholder="quote" name="quote">
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
    <h2>Quotes</h2>
    <ul class="quotes">
        <% for (let i=0; i<quotes.length; i++) {%>
            <li class="quote">
                <span>
                    <%= quotes[i].name %>:
                </span>
                <span>
                    <%= quotes[i].quote %>
                </span>
            </li>
         <% } %>
    </ul>
    <section>
        <h2>The trailer park supervisor</h2>
        <p>Mr. Lahey wants to clean up the trailer park and clear away any signs of criminal activity</p>
        <button id="update-button">Replace Ricky's words with liquor philosophy</button>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>The liquor</h2>
        <p>Perhaps giving Mr. Lahey a little teeny drink will make him happy?</p>
        <button id="delete-button">Don't go against the grain of the liquor</button>
    </section>
    <h4 id="message"></h4>
</body>
<script src="/main.js"></script>
</html>